These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, soccer, snowboarding
House: modern, gothic-revival, townhouse, art-deco
4 different games are played: billiard, snooker, domino, bridge
1. the person playing domino is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
2. the person playing bridge is the modern house##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1
5. the gothic-revival house is between the person playing domino and the person who's sport is rugby##2
6. the person playing snooker is the townhouse house##1
7. the modern house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Sport        | soccer | snowboarding  | rugby | rowing  |
| House         | art-deco    | gothic-revival  | modern       | townhouse     |
| Game   | domino     | billiard | bridge       | snooker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, pall-mall, montecristo, dunhill
4 different games are played: whist, mah-jongg, scrabble, monopoly
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, january, april, november
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person playing monopoly and the dunhill-smoker##2
5. the person playing monopoly is the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
7. the person playing scrabble is the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Cigar         | pall-mall | swisher    | dunhill  | montecristo |
| Game   | monopoly  | whist  | mah-jongg   | scrabble    |
| Birthday         | january | november | august | april      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, satire, romance, thriller
4 different games are played: scrabble, bridge, canasta, whist
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, airplane, helicopter, subway
1. the person driving the airplane is between the person driving the subway and the person watching satire movies##2
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing whist##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
7. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre      | satire | thriller         | musical   | romance    |
| Game         | bridge | whist | scrabble | canasta |
| Transport   | helicopter   | airplane        | subway      | motorbike   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, cooking, writing, baking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, romance, disaster, comedy
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, marigold, dahlia, bellflower
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the far left##1
2. the person who growslily is between the person who growsbellflower and the person who's hobby is baking##2
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person who growslily is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person who growsbellflower is between the person watching sports movies and the person who growsmarigold##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Hobby   | baking        | cooking   | sudoku | writing |
| Movie-Genre         | disaster | sports | romance    | comedy |
| Flower     | dahlia       | lily     | bellflower       | marigold    |

