.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, firefighter, mechanic, fisherman
House: colonial, victorian, craftsman, townhouse
There 4 different types of food: potato, orange, cucumber, radish
1. the person eating radish is between the paramedic and the firefighter##2
2. the person eating radish is the fisherman##1
3. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
4. the firefighter is on the left of the mechanic##1
5. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
6. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the victorian house##1
7. the person eating radish is between the person eating cucumber and the colonial house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Job   | paramedic | fisherman      | firefighter       | mechanic   |
| House      | colonial   | victorian  | townhouse | craftsman     |
| Food      | orange     | radish | cucumber        | potato |

