.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, manager, architect, teacher
4 different pets are kept: cat, horse, dog, goldfish
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, mirinda, cola, coffee
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the firefighter is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
3. the firefighter is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the manager##1
5. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the goldfish and the person drinking cola##2
6. the manager is between the firefighter and the architect##2
7. the person drinking tea is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Job    | architect | manager  | firefighter | teacher      |
| Pet   | dog  | goldfish  | cat | horse |
| Beverage   | coffee | tea | mirinda | cola     |

