.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, car, taxi, bus
City: marseilles, venice, miami, prague
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, fish, bird, goldfish
1. the owner of the goldfish is the person traveling to venice##1
2. the owner of the bird is the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the person traveling to miami is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the person driving the car is between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to miami##2
7. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Transport          | taxi  | car    | bus | ship  |
| City   | miami | prague       | venice        | marseilles    |
| Pet         | fish | hedgehog | goldfish  | bird |

