.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
City: marseilles, liverpool, new-york, hannover
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, soy-milk, milk, fanta
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, peach, asparagus, nectarine
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person eating nectarine and the person traveling to liverpool##2
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
4. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
6. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| City         | hannover  | liverpool | new-york | marseilles |
| Beverage   | tea  | fanta | soy-milk   | milk         |
| Food           | pineapple | asparagus  | peach   | nectarine      |

