The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, comedy, zombie, satire
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, biathlon, climbing
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is the bartender##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the fisherman##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is the fisherman##1
5. the bartender is on the right of the security-guard##1
6. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
7. the person watching comedy movies is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person watching fantasy movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Job          | security-guard  | bartender    | electrician | fisherman       |
| Movie-Genre         | satire | comedy | fantasy  | zombie |
| Sport   | biathlon   | climbing      | ice-hockey  | baseball     |

