.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, punk, hip-hop, d&b
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, designer, photographer, dancer
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, sprite, milk
1. the dancer is on the far left##1
2. the fan hip-hop is on the far left##1
3. the fan punk is between the fan country and the designer##2
4. the person drinking water is on the right of the fan d&b##1
5. the photographer is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking water is on the right of the fan d&b##1
7. the person drinking milk is the dancer##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is the fan d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Music-Genre          | hip-hop      | d&b | punk | country |
| Job         | dancer   | designer  | mechanic | photographer |
| Beverage   | milk | iced-tea   | water | sprite |

