The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, country, blues, indie
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, dannemann, aristoff, bongani
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is between the fan country and the fan blues##2
4. the fan blues is between the baccarat-smoker and the person who's birthday is in august##2
5. the fan blues is the bongani-smoker##1
6. the fan house is the dannemann-smoker##1
7. the fan indie is the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday    | august  | december | june | october     |
| Music-Genre   | house | blues   | indie  | country    |
| Cigar     | dannemann        | bongani       | baccarat      | aristoff |

