4. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
5. the indian is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
6. the oliveros-smoker is on the far right##1
7. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Nationality   | thai | australian     | indian | russian       |
| Game      | backgammon  | domino | bridge  | billiard |
| Cigar        | dunhill  | chaman      | swisher        | oliveros      |

