The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skateboarding, biathlon, handball
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, milk, hot-chocolate
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking milk is the person who likes pink##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who likes pink##2
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking lemonade is the person who likes blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Color           | lavender | blue | pink    | emerald   |
| Sport   | biathlon      | skateboarding   | handball | ice-hockey |
| Beverage     | 7up     | lemonade       | milk        | hot-chocolate    |

