.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-15::.
City: san-francisco, miami, new-york, paris
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, thriller, time-travel, scientific
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, grey, ivory, chestnut
1. the person traveling to new-york is the person who likes ivory##1
2. the person who likes chestnut is the person traveling to paris##1
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes grey is between the person watching zombie movies and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person who likes black##1
7. the person who likes black is between the person who likes chestnut and the person who likes grey##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| City   | new-york   | miami           | san-francisco         | paris      |
| Movie-Genre     | zombie | time-travel | scientific | thriller |
| Color   | ivory     | grey         | black       | chestnut        |

