.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
4 different games are played: whist, backgammon, chess, scrabble
4 different pets are kept: rat, hamster, frog, goat
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, skydiving, filmmaking, singing
1. the owner of the rat is the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing whist is between the person playing chess and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
3. the person playing chess is the owner of the hamster##1
4. the person playing chess is between the owner of the frog and the person who's hobby is singing##2
5. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing chess##1
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the owner of the goat##2
7. the owner of the rat is the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Game      | backgammon | chess | whist   | scrabble |
| Pet   | rat  | hamster    | frog   | goat     |
| Hobby   | singing  | filmmaking | traveling | skydiving   |

