There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, emerald, apricot, purple
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, havana, siglo, alhambra
1. the fan pop is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes apricot is between the fan r&b and the siglo-smoker##2
3. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the fan soul##1
6. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
7. the fan blues is the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | soul | r&b           | blues |
| Color       | fuchsia | apricot    | emerald          | purple   |
| Cigar      | siglo  | havana   | alhambra | ritmeester  |

