.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, gardening, woodworking, baking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, tennis, skiing, golf
4 different games are played: bridge, poker, scrabble, go
1. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is swimming##2
5. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the person playing go is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person playing bridge##2
7. the person who's sport is golf is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Hobby      | woodworking | magic-tricks | gardening     | baking   |
| Sport   | swimming | golf        | skiing  | tennis  |
| Game           | bridge      | go         | poker | scrabble |

