3. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the dog is the dannemann-smoker##1
5. the fan blues is the owner of the dog##1
6. the owner of the mouse is between the fan classical and the owner of the dog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Cigar         | bolivar        | dannemann  | pall-mall | old-henry   |
| Music-Genre       | indie | blues | country    | classical |
