.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, poppy, tulip, daffodil
House: cape-cod, modern, art-deco, futuristic
City: boston, liverpool, prague, london
1. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1
2. the person who growslily is on the right of the modern house##1
3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
4. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
5. the person traveling to london is the futuristic house##1
6. the modern house is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person traveling to prague##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Flower        | daffodil | poppy | lily | tulip |
| House         | cape-cod       | modern     | art-deco   | futuristic   |
| City   | boston | liverpool | prague | london |

 